      "title": "Holidays for schools till 20",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Education has announced that all government schools and government sanctioned schools will be given a holiday from July 18 to 20, and the new school term will begin on Thursday (21)."
      ],
